<P>
 Five people -- a couple and three children -- were found slain in a rural 
Mendocino County home, police said. Authorities have not yet determined if all 
five were members of the same family, said Willits police spokeswoman Barbara 
Hahn.But she said the victims were a man, a woman, two elementary school-age 
