<P>
 No criminal charges will be filed in connection with the death of a reserve 
police officer who was shot during a training exercise in Gilroy, Santa Clara 
County prosecutors said.Theodore Brassinga, 33, a Palo Alto reserve officer, 
died May 15 during a role-playing exercise designed to train police for the 
